{"tid":587261,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"傷者頭皮被鏟起縫21針","createTime":"2018-03-10T09:34:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-10T10:54:06.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"23003ae15dfdb867cab35a5e196a921997fb8bde","tid":587261,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T09:34:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180310/20327614\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180310%2F20327614&d=7TsPuvTwDarcJYwxYOrhW7%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=d07cbaac\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180310%2F20327614&h=043e3dbb\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180310/20327614</a><br />\n<br />\n傷者頭皮被鏟起縫21針<br />\n<br />\n要聞   <br />\n         <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180310/large/a0603a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180310%2Flarge%2Fa0603a.gif&h=a9e0ae6c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n意外發生後，有傷者頭皮被鏟起，倒卧大堂。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】朗豪坊通天梯案發時承載120人，驅動鏈「斷纜」後因失去向上拉力，電梯往下加速溜後，目擊者稱速度達正常的兩、三倍，導致底部乘客如骨牌倒下，多人堆叠。意外造成18人受傷，當中3人需留醫。控方昨披露有男子頭部重創，頭皮遭鏟起一片，更有女傷者需看心理醫生。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n女傷者需接受心理治療<br />\n<br />\n奧的斯認罪後，裁判官就判罰量刑查詢傷者傷勢，惟控方指傷者並非控告奧的斯疏忽保養的證人，故沒各人醫療報告，但據傷者的證人供詞，透露當中3名需留院傷者情況。<br />\n最嚴重的男傷者，頭頂頭皮遭鏟起需縫21針，腰背亦扭傷，手指腫脹，他留醫兩天，事後獲發一個半月病假。<br />\n<br />\n另一男傷者腳面有10厘米長傷痕需縫針，小腿及手部擦傷，獲發兩個月病假。另一名女傷者，除手背及腳跟有傷痕需縫針外，更需接受物理及心理治療。因辯方求情指傷者沒永久傷勢，裁判官一度詢問需否索創傷報告，以檢視女傷者精神上有否承受長遠影響，辯方回應稱不用。<br />\n<br />\n■記者伍嘉豪<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞<br />\n<br />\n\t技工「冇影」　紀錄卻顯示完成保養<br />\n要聞 7小時前<br />\n<br />\n\t共4日例檢無人到場　朗豪坊通天梯事故　奧的斯重罰32萬<br />\n要聞 7小時前"},{"pid":"6a6ca6df1daf8ba85c75e6f0fa2f25af83bb7e3d","tid":587261,"uid":3454,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T09:53:58.000Z","msg":"港嬸:好感恩........"},{"pid":"0c7776c306791ee72312cf73dffd7234474f3a47","tid":587261,"uid":164167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6a6ca6df1daf8ba85c75e6f0fa2f25af83bb7e3d","tid":587261,"uid":3454,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T09:53:58.000Z","msg":"港嬸:好感恩........"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T09:55:58.000Z","msg":"好彩係後生仔喺底到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d2f6dd67ecc224ed3fe67a6b18812ede1ce4b69","tid":587261,"uid":65984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T10:54:06.000Z","msg":"頭皮剷起成世禿頭, 呢次有排賠"}]}